# Your Shopify OAuth Credentials

**IMPORTANT: This file contains sensitive information. Do not commit to git!**

Add these lines to your `.env` file:

```env
# Shopify OAuth Configuration
SHOPIFY_CLIENT_ID=41bc4eaef71d627965ded15a8ec82c9e
SHOPIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=your_actual_secret_here
SHOPIFY_API_VERSION=2024-01
SHOPIFY_SCOPES=read_orders,read_products,read_customers
```

## How to Get Your Secret

1. Go to your Shopify app settings page (the one shown in your screenshot)
2. Click the eye icon or "Faire pivoter" button next to the Secret field
3. Copy the secret value
4. Paste it in your `.env` file replacing `your_actual_secret_here`

## OAuth Redirect URL

Add this to your Shopify app settings:
```
http://localhost/integrations/shopify/callback
```

Or for your production domain:
```
https://yourdomain.com/integrations/shopify/callback
```

